'''[[Yag Shushin]]'s star cruiser''' was a space freighter which had been captured by the [[Nightsisters/Legends|Nightsisters]] of [[Dathomir/Legends|Dathomir]] and modified as a [[subterine]] for underground travel. They used it to try to penetrate the [[Star Temple]].

